Comment.val:
/*This process will create batches of calculated fee header records based on a given jobid' without doing the actual processing. This is to enable the loadbalancing of the processing.
Per batch (range of calculated fee header records) a ServiceFeeBulkReportBatch message will be send.*/

ExpSyntax.val: FlwMtr('ERROR: During serviceFeeProcessing sending ''CreateServiceFeeBulkReprtBatch'' failed! Manually send message via ''JMS Interface/Unsent messages''.','FALSE'LOG)

SQL_STMT_U.val: select B.CFH_ID from ( select rownum my_row, A.CFH_ID from ( select cfh_id from calculated_fee_hdr where jobid = ~1 and CFH_STATE_ID=510 order by cfh_id asc)A ) B where MOD(B.my_row,~2)=0
